⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Grace
node ER · ER · ⟦Grace:ER:55ed17⟧

WHO   — Grace — the golden guidance of the Erdtree
WHAT  — The golden blessing of the Erdtree — favor's light in a Tarnished's eyes and the golden rays that point the way forward.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the frame  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Its return to the graceless Tarnished — guiding them back to war for the Ring — is the story's first mystery and the game's heartbeat.
HOW   — It marks the favored, gathers at sites of lost grace as guiding rays, and receives the dead to rise again — compass, checkpoint, and resurrection in one.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Die, and rise again at gold: the light that calls the graceless home to war.

